PHASE 7: WordPress Admin Enhancement
🎯 Objective
Modernize WordPress admin interface với consistent design system, enhanced functionality, at multi-location management capabilities based on Figma design: https://www.figma.com/community/file/1308435721888237413
📋 Dependencies

Phase 1: Design system CSS variables at base components
Phase 4: Portal dashboard components at analytics
Existing Backend: includes/class-admin.php, WordPress admin hooks

📦 Deliverables

modern-admin.css - WordPress admin styling
modern-admin.js - Admin interactions at enhancements
admin-dashboard.php - Super admin dashboard template
class-modern-admin.php - WordPress integration layer

🎨 Admin Interface Layout
